title: Fantasy Sleepers & Busts plus Mid-Round Draft Analysis with Dave Richard (Football 8/22)
description:
Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough fire up another 'Fantasy Week' podcast and are joined by CBS Sports fantasy football expert Dave Richard to share his thoughts on Amari Cooper and Ezekiel Elliott, before diving into sleepers, busts and issuing his thoughts on several mid-round RB & WR candidates.
